{"tid":299370,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知邊到有靚既貓跳台買","createTime":"2017-06-27T04:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T02:46:23.000Z","uid":107059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1222b5d674cbb89957af3e629554293393f12216","tid":299370,"uid":107059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/124413_48571870ae3c1da330a69eb55e62ee52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F124413_48571870ae3c1da330a69eb55e62ee52.jpg&h=6f701a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係類似呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知呢啲叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪叫貓跳台<br />\n我見旺角果啲都好似好細個又唔係好靚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港有無邊到有專門店賣呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1768777b7e7283c76aedf7a58a620dd4cfdd951","tid":299370,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"我明但係笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09f5957f5ce247010f15c24020d0c515d925eab","tid":299370,"uid":68079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"貓抓柱"},{"pid":"c0f6658a1eb69e3392d472529ee387d8d5235f13","tid":299370,"uid":122629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"8087497c68cbdfc7bd0bf229d4e14e1cf1605826","tid":299370,"uid":37916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"淘寶"},{"pid":"ff6c352ad5c9d10991e9427e970afe146ebc79be","tid":299370,"uid":12839,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"通常買完之後反而係對個紙皮箱最有興趣"},{"pid":"f18e5f5f717a948b62993b1356570d977f5921a3","tid":299370,"uid":13959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"淘寶search 貓樹"},{"pid":"4baf080ab2180faadfa87e2574ddef027a656a6b","tid":299370,"uid":75610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"貓樹"},{"pid":"7fef82dfdb40023a1cdc337188425c6809b341b5","tid":299370,"uid":1316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常買完之後反而係對個紙皮箱最有興趣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7190ff1dd883537c9ffa9dc8e979afd61f831a69","tid":299370,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常買完之後反而係對個紙皮箱最有興趣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5158ce604b60fae04bcbe220259990144c26e2c0","tid":299370,"uid":81850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"淘寶咩款都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef300beadba005cd940c31b2451bc1a80924b470","tid":299370,"uid":90969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常買完之後反而係對個紙皮箱最有興趣</blockquote><br />\n或者係啲膠袋,次次買完淘寶，將啲包裝袋塞埋一袋既時候，佢地就會想走入去。唔好咁啦好嗎？污糟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fb9c7c41636b0d9622d11a2dc591dcc51f1082","tid":299370,"uid":107059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明但係笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗左好耐都諗唔到呢啲叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1d4466a89152527c905555e4346ec776f82fdd","tid":299370,"uid":107059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常買完之後反而係對個紙皮箱最有興趣</blockquote><br />\n屋企一有紙箱紙袋佢就跳入去玩到癲左咁<br />\n不過其實係因為屋企果條抓柱太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想順便換過條"},{"pid":"4560d2057e21243174475210f403f06a92d94c38","tid":299370,"uid":107059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶search 貓樹</blockquote><br />\nThank you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bbfc757e704a57f65d4946c9a1ded0cfce6e15","tid":299370,"uid":107059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓抓柱</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知道 thank you"},{"pid":"1378c90dac1f45c24293cf812aee87b340dddc89","tid":299370,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"有毛好吸塵架 香港見過有台灣木全製既 但好拎貴 成2000蚊 淘寶應該會平d<br />\n但買木製品小心會有蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695e40f59cddee0fe879ce56c741d8c8b0cd1b0d","tid":299370,"uid":45526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:25:58.000Z","msg":"香港潮濕真係唔係好建議人買呢種樹，一踩屎再跳上去就gg。我屋企用木貓樹，淘寶買，用左成年都好掂，無蟲無任何野，好硬淨。不過貓大左後，都無再爬過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8920674e76bdde8db5e2eaa56ebef7b63b5294","tid":299370,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:25:10.000Z","msg":"見到韓國出個啲貓柱勁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但超貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999e74ce920c4d584274773ab207308856507d74","tid":299370,"uid":108103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/045254_3ce4ebe0442a890480095305551730b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F045254_3ce4ebe0442a890480095305551730b0.jpg&h=1c725b32&s={SIZE}\" /> 屋企用咁呢隻 好受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e532802e3efa4369396022807a9cb2619c30c7a6","tid":299370,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/045254_3ce4ebe0442a890480095305551730b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F045254_3ce4ebe0442a890480095305551730b0.jpg&h=1c725b32&s={SIZE}\" /> 屋企用咁呢隻 好受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同邊度買"},{"pid":"2ed2b3901ca43ca0a9746ea94f94bd4d7a40297e","tid":299370,"uid":107844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T23:19:49.000Z","msg":"自己整，三個紙皮箱整啲窿再疊起仲岩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cfbed803655ad0202c32599a03e8f56653a92d","tid":299370,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}